    "causal_summary": "Standalone Media Editor skill for Barter that edits, converts, compresses and streams existing images, video and audio. Routes every request into one of five intents (Image, Video, Audio, HLS, Repair) through an exact-command then semantic-keyword detection sequence, binds and verifies the required tool (Imagician MCP, Video-Audio MCP or Terminal FFmpeg) before any operation, applies the MEDIA thinking framework, and exports a verified result before responding. It matters because it is the one discoverable identity for Barter media editing work, keeping tool-capability promises honest and deliverables saved and verified before every response.",
